data.meta_description: Match Report11 - Free download as Word Doc (.doc), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This match summary provides the score and key details of a soccer match between teams from Angola and Morocco in the 14th African U-20 Championship. Morocco defeated Angola 1-0, with the sole goal scored by player Iajour Mouhssine in the 39th minute. There were multiple substitutions and cautions issued to players from both teams for unsporting behavior and protesting referee decisions.
